•   ATLANTA, GA
                          • Investment Advisor
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Capital Directions Investment Advisors is based out of Atlanta. Capital Directions Investment Advisors is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $1,326,000,000 (Form ADV from 2017-02-21).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $288,861,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 89.15%. Capital Directions Investment Advisors's largest holding is SPDR Series Trust - SPDR S&P 500 Growth ETF with shares held of 650,925.  Capital Directions Investment Advisors has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 37 13F filings in our database for Capital Directions Investment Advisors. 
                                           






