We currently do not have enough data to calculate a rating for this plan.















Plan Description
        
Capital Directions LLC 401K Profit Sharing Plan is a defined contribution plan with a profit-sharing component and 401k feature. Capital Directions LLC 401K Profit Sharing Plan currently has fewer than 100 active participants and over $2.3M in plan assets. 

        




